"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Another way to reduce gas fees is to use a layer 2 network or sidechain:\\n\\n1. **Layer 1** **network** is the main Ethereum blockchain.\\n2. **Layer 2 networks** process transactions off-chain before bundling and submitting them to the Ethereum blockchain. They benefit from Ethereum's security and distributed network. [Arbitrum](https://arbitrum.io/) is an example of a layer 2 network.\\n3. **Sidechains** are separate blockchains that use their own token to pay for gas. You can move tokens between sidechains and Ethereum through a **bridge**. [Polygon](https://polygon.technology/) is an example of a sidechain.\\n\\nLayer 2 networks and sidechains offer much lower gas fees than the main Ethereum blockchain (e.g., $0.0001 vs. $80). We'll cover how to use these platforms in our NFT and DeFi learning paths.\",\"timestamp\":1642669731,\"title\":\"Layer 2 networks and sidechains\"},\"digest\":\"ic93UFsGYm0_Jka7hrH4L4CrtJryp5gjiiF_3-i1qBA\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xD1776912A399F3709928ba7E53b19c9E4e13181D\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"xF1UiczjJFdH2nBZxpsrLBIijRltrev6jbNG0ffJgYo\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"3WdMwkXWnsI86f7B4feNsDbgyTm_FwOAln-6PFCAYx0\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"iNN2SBiAP4qV3RLXWHk5F1LL2OMEtx_1dZbuf6Qa7X5Wg-WRo-hCjcEEHBY_2FkJWB1uxApZCP48456QIZCBsQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x2a66cd6b55a4f8cb3dd8e6b9fe5c6008d5245a518b4df9718363d3f3370140b12c284cdd2e9c7df02cb31413b78e68ec3a0a01dce686cb1b6414991b5a33b2051c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"xF1UiczjJFdH2nBZxpsrLBIijRltrev6jbNG0ffJgYo\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"3WdMwkXWnsI86f7B4feNsDbgyTm_FwOAln-6PFCAYx0\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"ic93U